OL,7,FA "Brexit pubs guarantee" will see the
OL,8,Fduty on draught pints in pubs set up to
OL,9,F11p lower than the duty in supermarkets
OL,10,Ffrom August, the Chancellor said.
OL,12,FDraught Relief will reduce the tax
OL,13,Fburden on qualifying alcoholic products
OL,14,Fsold in on-trade venues, such as pubs,
OL,15,Ffrom draught containers containing at
OL,16,Fleast 20 litres.
OL,18,FHowever, alcohol duties will still rise
OL,19,Fwith inflation ` at the same time as
OL,20,Fthe Government reforms the levies based
OL,21,Fon a drink's alcoholic strength.
OL,3,CAlcohol tax on pints in pubs up to 11p
OL,4,Clower than in supermarkets from August,
OL,5,Csays Hunt
